00:04:01.830 --> 00:04:03.440
A number that we can use,
a whole number.

00:04:03.440 --> 00:04:06.490
So what we'll do is on this
side, we'll go 5 plus 2 by the

00:04:06.490 --> 00:04:08.160
square root of 2 by the square
root of 3, and now

00:04:08.160 --> 00:04:09.970
