00:04:09.970 --> 00:04:12.650
So we'll end up getting 2 by
the square root of 2 by the

00:04:12.650 --> 00:04:13.470
square root of 3.

00:04:13.470 --> 00:04:15.560
And this is good, because
there's no

00:04:15.560 --> 00:04:17.060
plus sign in the middle.

00:04:17.060 --> 00:04:18.079
What can we do next?

00:04:18.079 --> 00:04:20.339
Well, we're going to
square all of that.

00:04:20.339 --> 00:04:25.400
So 2 squared is 4, and the
